transcript: - (Justine) Hey guys it's Justine and today I am going to be making a Fortnite Cake, (uptempo music) and this is going to be celebrating Season 3 because Season 4 is upon us or it's actually already out depending upon when you're watching this. This is going to be my Season 3 cake. I am really excited because I just started playing this game, and it was one of those games that I really avoided playing because I knew that it was something that would take up all of my free time. So if you guys were wondering "Justine why haven't you been posting YouTube videos", it's because I've been playing Fortnite. Why don't I stream Fortnite--because I like to just sit in my pajamas, with Doritos on my belly and be left alone! And I like to play my game and not have to talk to anybody except my teammates, sometimes unless I'm playing solo, then I'm just... dying a lot... Anyway I'm excited about the cake but I'm also giving myself a time constraint, so basically while I'm building the cake, the storm is incoming, so if I don't finish by the time the storm gets to me, I'm not really sure what's gonna happen. This is the first one I'm making so, stay tuned, because your guess is as good as mine. Currently while I'm shooting this, I don't have any information on Season 4 so depending upon when you guys are watching you probably already know everything about it. This is me, this is me in Loot Lake (laughs) swimming. Okay shut up Justine. (quick beep noise) Okay let's make this freaking cake.
